\pard\fi0\li0\qj\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 12\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 r-v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  \plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24 Exzerpte zur {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezwrk[0].6930/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 theologia mystica}}\plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24 : {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezper[0].4100/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Johannes de Castello}}\plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24 , {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezper[1].4100/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Johannes Cassianus}}\plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24 , {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezper[2].4100/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Hermannus Reinboth}}\plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24 , {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezper[3].4100/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Hugo de S. Victore}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 .
\par \pard\fi0\li0\qj\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 (a) \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 Item Albertus de adherendo deo capitulo decimo: Cogita semper in eternitate anime tue in deo ...\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 capitulo xii\plain \f2\i\lang1024\fs24 \u176 \'b0\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24  ... hic Albertus Magnus\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 in libellus de adhaerendo deo ...\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ;\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24  \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 (b) \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 Item abbas Ysaac ita scribens ait: Tunc erimus unum in deo ...\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ; (12\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ) (c) \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 Item \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 [gestrichen: \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 pater Hermannus Reynbott quondam prior et visitator principalis in Norimberga\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ]\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24  in quadam collacione \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 [gestrichen: \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 facta\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ] \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 pro capitulo generali \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 [gestrichen: \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 ab eo comportata\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ]\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24  qui incipit: Omne datum optimum etc. \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 (Iac 1,17)\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 . Clamante thuba apostolica concurrente auctoritate omni katholice fidei doctorum maxime beati Dyonisii Aryopagite in \u8218 \'82De angelica yerarchia\rquote  et eciam magni doctoris in ,De docta ignorancia\rquote  omnia ab uno per unum et in uno consistere constat ...\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ;\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24  \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 (d) \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 Quia secundum Hugonem de sancto Victore super ,De celesti ierarchia\rquote  ipsa data optima ...\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  - \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 ... in illius forma omnes unum apparerent. Hic ille. \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 [die letzten 6 Zeilen gestrichen, Kommentar zum Thema \u8218 \'82infinitas essentiae divinae\rquote :] \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 In verbis istis thematis ... est infinitum. Sed sic est \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 [..., bricht ab.
