\pard\fi0\li0\qj\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 44\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 -46\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  \plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24 Exzerptsammlung zum {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezwrk[0].6930/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Unterschied zwischen theologia mystica und theologia speculativa}}\plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24 : {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezper[0].4100/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Robertus Grosseteste}}\plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24 , {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezper[1].4100/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Thomas Vercellensis}}\plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24 , {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezper[2].4100/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Hugo de s. Victore}}\plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24 , {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezper[3].4100/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Nicolaus de Cusa}}\plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24 , {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezper[4].4100/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Johannes de Castello}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 .
\par \pard\fi0\li0\qj\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 Sciendum quod supradicta scripta dicta sunt non secundum theologiam misticam sed secundum theologiam speculatiuam et communem qui est secundum intellectum et non secundum affectum scilicet amorem.\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ;\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24  \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 (a) \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 Unde egregius doctor Robertus librorum sancti Dyonisii translator \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 [= \plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24 Robertus Grosseteste\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ]\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24  in suo commento dicit: Cum plerumque circa divina contigit errare ...\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ;\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24  \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 (b) \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 Cui contestans Thomas Vercellensis super mistica theologia dicens: Quia deus non potest cognosci per intellectualem cognicionem ...\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ;\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24  \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 (c) \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 Venerabilis Hugo libro viii super celesti ierarchia \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 [45\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 r-v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  Schaltzettel, s. u.] (46\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 r\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ) \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 beati Dionysii dicit: Ut intelligas vim amoris et dilectionis ... \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 - \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 ... hoc idem ipsum sit quod ipse. Hic Hugo\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ;\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24  \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 (d) \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 Quapropter sancti doctores et viri illuminatissimi maxime Dyonysius suique translatores et commentatores specialissime eciam Nicolaus Cusa in suis libris et scriptis excelentissimis ...\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ;\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24  \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 (e) \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 Item Albertus Magnus in libello {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezwrk[2].6930/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 de adherendo deo}}\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24  cap. ix: Animadvertenda inquit est etiam in hoc differentia ...\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  - \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 ... ac per hanc ad lucem incessabilem.
\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 Zu (a) und (b) s. o. 35\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 r\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ; (c) \plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24 Hugo de s. Victore, {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezwrk[1].6930/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Expositio in Hierarchiam coelestem s. Dionysii Areopagitae}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , vgl. Druck: PL 175, Sp. 1038D-1039A; (e) Edition: (s. o. 12\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 r\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ), S. 532f.}

