\pard\fi0\li0\qj\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 48\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 -53\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 v\plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24  Exzerptsammlung zum Thema {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezwrk[0].6930/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Seele als Ebenbild Gottes}}\plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24 : {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezper[0].4100/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Petrus Lombardus}}\plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24 , {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezper[1].4100/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Augustinus}}\plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24 , {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezper[2].4100/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Jan van Schoonhoven}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ,\plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24  {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezper[3].4100/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Ps.-Bertramus de Ahlen}}\plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24 , {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezper[4].4100/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Bonaventura}}\plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24 , {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezper[5].4100/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Bernardus Claraevallensis}}\plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24 , {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezper[6].4100/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Hugo de Balma}}\plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24  etc\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 . 
\par \pard\fi0\li0\qj\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 Et ergo non incongrue insistendum esse videtur ut homo studeat se ipsum cognoscere et quidditatem anime sue investigare. \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 (a) \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 Magister Sententiarum: Flatus quo deus hominem animauit id est hominem fecit ...\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ; (b) \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 Augustinus in libro de quantitate anime: Anima facta est similis deo ...\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ;\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24  \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 (c) \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 Dicit Johannes de Schonhauia: Est sciendum inquit quod creature preexistunt in mente divina siue in \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 (49\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 r\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ) \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 deo simpliciter ...\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ;\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24  \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 (d) \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 Item Bertramus in libello de investigatione creatoris in creaturis dicit: Sic et homo quasi per speculum in se ipso id est in sua essencia videt deum ...\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ;\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24  \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 (e) \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 Quia ut Bonaventura in suo itinerario mentis in deum capitulo 3\plain \f1\i\super\lang1033\fs24 o\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24  dicit de duobus gradibus per quos ducamur in deum ...\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ; (f)\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24  Bernardus super cantica: Non potest deo acceptius esse imagine sua ...\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ; (g) \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 Item Augustinus de Genesi ad litteram vi: Quid habet homo excellentius nisi quod ipse ad imaginem dei creatus est? ... Augustinus in retractacione eiusdem libri: Hanc ymaginem inquit in spiritu mentis impressam \u8230 \'85\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ; (49\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ) \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 \u8230 \'85 \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 (h) \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 Idem affirmat magister Sententiarum libro i distinctione 27 conclusione v: Omnia dicuntur in deo esse \u8230 \'85\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ; (50\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 r\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ) [Einf\u252 \'fcgung des Kompilators:] \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 Superius variis in locis cepi tractare et scribere de fundo et abisso spiritus ... \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 (i) \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 Unde in quadam collacione de sancta Maria Magdalena in libro de triplici via sub littera D 18 sic scriptum reperi: Secunda contemplacio veritatis est ... Item in eodem libro folio 200b ... \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 [marginal eingef\u252 \'fcgt:\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24  folio 204a\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ]\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24  In deserto mentis nostre est libertas quedam ...\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ; (50\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ) \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 \u8230 \'85 \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 (j) \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 Quidam homo divinus in oracione semper dicebat: O non inclusum intraneum, o non latens secretum \u8230 \'85\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ; (52\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 r\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ) \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 \u8230 \'85 \plain \f2\lang1024\fs24 [\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 Zusammenfassung des Kompilators:\plain \f2\lang1024\fs24 ]\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 (Recapitulacio) \plain \f2\lang1024\fs24 [\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 marginal eingef\u252 \'fcgt: \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 prima \plain \f2\lang1024\fs24 ]\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 Dixi iam superius quod in intimitatem anime nulla creatura potest intrare \u8230 \'85 \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 (52\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ) \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 \u8230 \'85 Recapitulacio secunda \u8230 \'85\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ; (53\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 r\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 )\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24  ...\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  (k) \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 Quadruplex est regio anime in hac mortali vita \u8230 \'85\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ; (l) \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 Dicit Bonaventura in suo itinerario mentis in deum quod omnes scientie habent regulas certas \u8230 \'85\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ;\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24  \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 (53\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 )\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24  ...\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  (m) \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 Item Augustinus: Ego quidem ammonitus intraui in intima mea ... \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 - \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 ... O eterna veritas et vera eternitas cui suspiro die ac nocte.
\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 Neben gliedernden Textpassagen des Kompilators zahlreiche, z. T. kurze Exzerpte, u. a.: (a) \plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24 Petrus Lombardus\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezwrk[1].6930/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Sententiae in IV libris distinctae}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , lib. 2, dist. 17/1; (b) \plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24 Augustinus\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezwrk[2].6930/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 De quantitate animae}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , Edition: CSEL 89; (c) \plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24 Jan van Schoonhoven\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , evtl. Auszug aus der {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezwrk[3].6930/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Commendatio sive defensio libri fratris Johannis Ruusbroec}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , s. u. 235\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ; (d) Ps.-\plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24 Bertramus de Ahlen,\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezwrk[4].6930/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 De investigatione creatoris in creaturis}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , cap. 27, Edition: A. \plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24 Beccarisi\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  (Hg.), Miscellanea, Texte aus der Zeit Meister Eckharts, Bd. 2: Berthold von Wimpfen; Ps. Bertram von Ahlen, Hamburg 2004 (Corpus philosophorum Teutonicorum medii aevi 7,2), S. 308; (e) \plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24 Bonaventura\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezwrk[5].6930/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Itinerarium mentis in deum}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , cap. III,1, Edition: Tria opuscula Seraphici Doctoris S. Bonaventurae, Quaracchi 1925, S. 314; (f) \plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24 Bernardus Claraevallensis\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezwrk[6].6930/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Sermones super Cantica Canticorum}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , sermo 25, pars 7, Edition: S. Bernardi Opera 1, S. 167; (g) \plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24 Augustinus\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezwrk[7].6930/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 De Genesi ad litteram}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , lib. VI,12, VI,27, Edition: CSEL 28,1, S. 187, 199; (h) \plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24 Petrus Lombardus\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezwrk[1].6930/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Sententiae in IV libris distinctae}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , lib. 1, dist. 35, cap. 9, par. 1; (i) \plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24 Hugo de Balma\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezwrk[8].6930/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Theologia mystica vel De triplici via}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , Edition (als Werk Bonaventuras): Bonaventura, Opera omnia, Bd. 8 (1898), S. 2-27; zum Autor und zur Rezeptionsgeschichte vgl. H. \plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24 Walach\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , Notitia experimentalis Dei - Erfahrungserkenntnis Gottes, Studien zu Hugo de Balmas Text \u8222 \'84Viae Sion lugent\rdblquote  und dt. \u220 \'dcbersetzung, Salzburg 1994 (Analecta Cartusiana 98,1); im Bibliothekskatalog der Erfurter Kartause die erw\u228 \'e4hnte Hs. unter der Signatur D 20 aufgef\u252 \'fchrt [Verbleib der Hs. unbekannt], vgl. MBK II, S. 322\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 25\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 -324\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 20\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , hier mit dem Titel \u8222 \'84De triplici via anime in Deum [\plain \f2\lang1024\fs24 \u188 \'bc\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ] tractatus compositus per quendam Carthusiensem, qui dictus est Hugo de Palma\rdblquote , als Inhalt u. a. \u8222 \'84Sermo de b. Maria Magdalena, docens quomodo devota anima Deum querat et incipit [\plain \f2\lang1024\fs24 \u188 \'bc\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ]\rdblquote , das Werk des Hugo de Balma auch \u252 \'fcberliefert in den Hss. D 2 und D 11\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 3\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  der Erfurter Kartause, vgl. MBK II, S. 302\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 3-10\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , 314\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 23f.\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ; (j) und (k) nicht identifiziert; (l) \plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24 Bonaventura\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezwrk[5].6930/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Itinerarium mentis in deum}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , cap. III,7, Edition: (s. o. \plain \f2\lang1024\fs24 [\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 e\plain \f2\lang1024\fs24 ]\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ), S. 323; (m) \plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24 Augustinus\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezwrk[9].6930/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Confessiones}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  VII,10.16, Edition: CCSL 27; S. 103.}

