\pard\fi0\li0\qj\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 (67\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , 69\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 r\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ) {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezper[0].4100/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 John Mandeville}}\plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24 , {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezwrk[0].6930/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Itinerarium}}\plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24 , \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 lat. \u220 \'dcbersetzung,\plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24  \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 Exzerpt aus cap. 5, 37: \plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24 Landweg zum Hl. Land\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 . 
\par \pard\fi0\li0\qj\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 \plain \f2\lang1024\fs24 [\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 marginale Notiz des Schreibers:\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24  Hic notatur una uia siue iter ad terram sanctam sine passagio per mare \u8230 \'85 scilicet pedester.\plain \f2\lang1024\fs24 ]\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 Item in itinerario magistri de Mandeuelde parte prima capitulo v dicit de una via per quam omnino mare transeundum ad terram sanctam non est necessarium videlicet si per Alemaniam per Bohemiam, per Prussiam, hinc per terram paganorum regni Laycon \plain \f2\lang1024\fs24 [\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 sonst: Lituaniae\plain \f2\lang1024\fs24 ]\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 , et sic per longam et pessimam terram prime Tartarie usque in Indiam ...\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  \plain \f2\lang1024\fs24 [\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 Schaltzettel 68\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 r-v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  s. u.\plain \f2\lang1024\fs24 ]\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 \u8230 \'85 - \u8230 \'85 \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 (69\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 r\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ) \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 ... Hinc usque hodie omnes successores paganismo fedantur. \plain \f2\lang1024\fs24 [\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 Bemerkung des Kompilators:\plain \f2\lang1024\fs24 ]\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 Anno autem domini M ccc xxiii tempore isto fuit magister Johannes de Mandeuilla in Tartaria tunc regnauit unus imperator ibidem et dicebatur Grancan \plain \f2\lang1024\fs24 [\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 = Gand Can, s. o. 64\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 r\plain \f2\lang1024\fs24 ]\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 . Et primogenitus eius Causie Can \plain \f2\lang1024\fs24 [\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 sonst: Cosuecan\plain \f2\lang1024\fs24 ]\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 , preter quem et alios filios habuit xxii. De legibus et moribus istorum Tartarorum qui sunt sub imperio Grancan nota eundem magistrum Johannem de Mandeuilla in itinerario suo parte secunda capitulo 39. 
\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 Edition und Literatur s. o. 57\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 .}

