\par \pard\fi0\li0\qj\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 (73\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 r\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ) (a) \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 De Tartarorum regni principium \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 (!) \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 legitur in complemento cronicarum: Circa annum domini 1203 Dauid quidam Persa ex ignobili familia ...\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ; \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 Nota in ultima parte Speculi historialis libro xxx\u176 \'b0 de Tartaris a lxix usque ad xc capitulum exclusiue ibi ualde luculenter habetur de gente Tartarorum et de institucione eorum. Item de Tamburlano magno Tartarorum seu Parthorum rege ... in quartodecimo libro Supplementi chronicarum ...\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ; (b) \plain \f2\lang1024\fs24 [\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 Exzerpt aus \u8218 \'82Supplementum chronicarum\rquote  und anderen Quellen mit Kommentar des Kompilators:\plain \f2\lang1024\fs24 ]\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 Unde capitulo lxxxix ista reperi de montibus Caspie ... Unum quod in dubium michi uenit inferre uolo: Quando enim dicant historie nostre scholastice ... \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 (73\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 )\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24  ... Item Xsansa domino Tartarorum. Der Thuchger nennet den fyerden den Usane Cassan. Ego estimo, quod sit ille quartus qui dicitur Sumcassianus de quo infra. \plain \f2\lang1024\fs24 [\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 s. o. 72\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 r\plain \f2\lang1024\fs24 ]\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 Sarracenorum triplex est differencia. Quidam enim vocantur Thurcomanni et hii morantur ad plagam Aquiloniem ciuitatis Ierusalem ... Quidam uero appellantur Marrochiani et hii inhabitant Affricam magnam ... Alii vero nuncupantur Soldanini et hii inhabitant terram promissionis ...
\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 (a) {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezper[0].4100/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Vincentius Bellovacensis}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezwrk[1].6930/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Speculum historiale}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , pars IV, lib. 30, cap. 69-90, s. o. 64\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 r\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ; zur Legende Davids, Sohn des \u8222 \'84Priesterk\u246 \'f6nigs\ldblquote  Johannes, vgl. M. \plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24 M\plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24 \u252 \'fc\plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24 nkler\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , Erfahrung des Fremden. Die Beschreibung Ostasiens in den Augenzeugenberichten des 13. und 14. Jahrhunderts, Berlin 2000, S. 22 u.\u246 \'f6.; (b)\plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24  J{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezper[1].4100/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 acobus Philippus Foresti}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezwrk[2].6930/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Supplementum Chronicarum}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  (s. o. 54\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ), lib. XIV, cap. 87-89, s. o. 54\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 .}

