\par \pard\fi0\li0\qj\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 (76\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ) (a) \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 Ethyopia. Ethyopia consistit in terra Chaldeorum in austrum que distinguitur ...\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ; (77\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 r\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ) (b) \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 Regio seu insula dicta Lumbe \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 [sonst: Lombe] \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 in India superiori spatiosa quidem est ...\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ; (c) \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 Reuertendo itaque quasi per Aquilonare latus imperii presbiteri Johannis \u8230 \'85\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ; (d) \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 Item. Est una insula in India ubi habitant gigantes ad staturam altitudinis viginti quinque pedum nostrorum ...\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ; (e) \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 Item in predicta insula Casso \plain \f2\lang1024\fs24 [\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 sonst: Kaffa\plain \f2\lang1024\fs24 ]\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 quicumque illic infirmari videtur ad mortem \u8230 \'85\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ; (f) \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 Item in regione Doudun\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  \plain \f2\lang1024\fs24 [\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 sonst: Doudin\plain \f2\lang1024\fs24 ]\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 cuius rex principatur 54 regibus \u8230 \'85\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ;\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24  \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 (77\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ) \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 \u8230 \'85 \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 (g) \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 Hinc meridiem pluribus exactis insulis per viam decem dietarum venitur\u8230 \'85\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 - \u8230 \'85 in ciuitate Calamie seruatur in magno templo corpus beatissimi Thome apostoli. Nota ibi in itinerario Johannis de Mandauilla folio 346\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ;\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24  \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 (h) \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 Inde vlterius procedendo in austrum per multas et mirabiles terras \u8230 \'85\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ; (i) \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 Item tempore Karoli \plain \f2\lang1024\fs24 [\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 sonst: magni regis Franciae\plain \f2\lang1024\fs24 ]\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 dux Ogerus Danorum armata manu conquisiuit christianitati fere omnes partes transmarinas \u8230 \'85\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ; (j)\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24  Circa has arbores solis excolitur balsamum \u8230 \'85 - \u8230 \'85 dicuntur illorum virtute quadringentis aut pluribus annis viuere.
