\pard\fi0\li0\qj\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 91\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 -96\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  \plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24 Exzerpte und Schemata zum Thema {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezwrk[0].6930/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 \u8218 \'82De caelis}}\plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24  / {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezwrk[1].6930/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 De sphaeris\rquote }}\plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24 : {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezper[0].4100/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Isidorus Hispalensis}}\plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24 ; {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezper[1].4100/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Moses Maimonides}}\plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24 ; {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezper[2].4100/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Beda Venerabilis}}\plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24 , {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezper[3].4100/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Thomas Cantimpratensis}}\plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24  etc.
\par \pard\fi0\li0\qj\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 (91\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ) (a)\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24  Ysidorus. Legimus in Dauid: Laudate eum celi celorum ... \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 (Ps 148,4).\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24  Et Paulus usque ad celum tercium intelligit fuisse se raptum. Fecit itaque Deus celos non informes uel confusos ...\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ; (91\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , 93\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 r\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ) (b)\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24  Item Rabi Moyses: In tempore Aristotelis non fuit verificatus numerus celorum ...\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ; \plain \f2\lang1024\fs24 [\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 Schaltzettel 92\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 r-v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , s. u.\plain \f2\lang1024\fs24 ]\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ; (93\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 r-v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ) (c)\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24  De ethere. Quid autem etheris nomine iuxta Bedam significetur \u8230 \'85\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ; (93\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ) (d)\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24  Item in addicione Burgensis episcopi super Liram \u8230 \'85; \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 (93\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 -94\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 r\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ) (e) \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 Axis est septentrionalis linea recta, que per mediam pylam spere tendit \u8230 \'85\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ; (94\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 r\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 -95\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ) (f) \plain \f2\lang1024\fs24 [\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 De sphaeris caeli\plain \f2\lang1024\fs24 ]\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 Zone celi uel arculi sic dicti sunt: \u8230 \'85 - \u8230 \'85 Hic Ysidorus\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ; darin eingef\u252 \'fcgt (94\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ) Schema (9,5 x 8,5 cm): Sph\u228 \'e4ren des Himmels und Sternzeichen; (95\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 -96\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 r\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ) (g)\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24  Itaque celi motum orbicularem ab oriente supra terram in occidentem ...\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ; (96\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 r-v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ) (h)\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24  Sol quidem et luna luminaria magna dicuntur non quod maiora sunt corpore uel lumine apud se ...\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ; (96\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ) (i)\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24  Terra ut dicit philosophus est corpus simplum \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 (!)\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24  in loco medio situ \u8230 \'85 - \u8230 \'85 non in terram sed in caelum caderent etc.
\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 (a) \plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24 Isidorus Hispalensis\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezwrk[2].6930/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 De natura rerum}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , cap. 13, vgl. PL 83, Sp. 986A-987A; (b) Rabbi \plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24 Moses Maimonides\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezwrk[3].6930/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Speculum naturale}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  III \plain \f2\lang1024\fs24 [\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 IV\plain \f2\lang1024\fs24 ]\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , 82; (c) \plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24 Beda Venerabilis\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezwrk[4].6930/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 De temporum ratione}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , cap. 32; (d) {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezper[4].4100/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Paulus de Burgos}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezwrk[5].6930/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Additiones ad postillam Nicolai de Lyra super Biblia}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , s. u. 96\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ; (e, f) \plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24 Isidorus Hispalensis\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezwrk[6].6930/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Etymologiae}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  III,36-42,4, 44,1-4, Edition: (s. o. 53\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ), Bd. 1, S. 150f., 152; (h) wohl angelehnt an: \plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24 Thomas Cantimpratensis\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezwrk[7].6930/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Liber de natura rerum}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  17,9, vgl. Edition Berlin, New York 1973, S. 394; (i) mit Verweis auf {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezper[5].4100/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Macrobius}}\plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24  Ambrosius Theodosius\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezwrk[8].6930/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Commentarii in somnium Scipionis}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  I,22,10 und {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezper[6].4100/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Honorius Augustodunensis}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezwrk[9].6930/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Imago mundi}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 .}

