\pard\fi0\li0\qj\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 98\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 -100\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezwrk[0].6930/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 De situ paradisi}}\plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24 , Exzerptsammlung\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 .
\par \pard\fi0\li0\qj\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 De paradiso. \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 (a) \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 Lyra ut supra. Plantaverat dominus ... \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 (Gn 2,8)\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24  scilicet tercio die quando primo producte \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 (99\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 r\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ) \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 sunt plante et hebrei hec dicunt. \u8218 \'82In oriente\rquote ...\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ; (99\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 r\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 -100\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 r\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ) (b) \plain \f2\lang1024\fs24 [\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 Zusammenstellung der Meinungen verschiedener Autorit\u228 \'e4ten:\plain \f2\lang1024\fs24 ]\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 Omnes autem qui loquuntur de situ paradisi terrestris ponunt eum esse in partibus orientis \plain \f2\i\lang1024\fs24 \u188 \'bc\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24  Philosophus enim in Metheororum dicit ...\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 Alii vero dicunt quod inter duos tropicos subequinoctiali circulo est regio temperantissima, quod eciam asserit frater Johannes de Pecham in tractatu suo de spera pluribus racionibus quas propter prolixitatem hic obmitto ... Et Burgensis ibidem in addicione ... Ad hoc eciam respondit Mathias Dorinck in replica \u8230 \'85 \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 (99\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ) \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 \u8230 \'85 Item in uitas patrum per impressum folio lxxvii in vita sancti Macharii Romani qui inuentus est iuxta paradisum \u8230 \'85 \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 - \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 ... pervenerunt ad Persiam regionem etc.\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ; (100\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 r-v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ) (c) \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 Item de paradiso in itinerario magistri Johannis de Mandeuelde habetur sic: A finibus imperii Indie recta linea in orientem nihil est habitatum vel habitabile ... - ... nisi forte uolatilibus prout decreuit iusti iudicii deus.
\par \pard\fi0\li0\qj\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 (a) {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezper[0].4100/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Nicolaus de Lyra}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 : {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezwrk[1].6930/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Postilla litteralis in Vetus et Novum Testamentum}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , s. o. 96\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ; (b) erw\u228 \'e4hnt werden u. a.: (99\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 r\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ) {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezper[1].4100/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Aristoteles}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezwrk[2].6930/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Meterologica}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ; {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezper[2].4100/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Johannes Peckham}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezwrk[3].6930/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 De sphaera}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ; {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezper[3].4100/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Paulus de Burgos}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezwrk[4].6930/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Additiones ad Postillam}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  (s. o. 96\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ); {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezper[4].4100/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Matthias D\u246 \'f6ring}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezwrk[5].6930/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Replicae defensivae}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  (s. o. 96\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ); {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezper[5].4100/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Isidorus Hispalensis}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezwrk[6].6930/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Etymologiae}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ; (99\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ) Folioangabe \u252 \'fcbereinsteimmend mit dem Druck: Vitas patrum, N\u252 \'fcrnberg: Anton Koberger, 7.V.1478 (vgl. GW M50876, eingesehenes Exemplar: Leipzig, UB, Editt. Vett. 1478,11); (c) {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezper[6].4100/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 John Mandeville}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezwrk[7].6930/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Itinerarium}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , cap. 48, Edition und Literatur s. o. 57\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 .
\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 98\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  am Textanfang und am unteren Rand Vermerke des Schreibers: \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 Nota eciam superius ante xvii folia\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  und \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 Item de paradiso nota inferius post xiii folia.}

