\pard\fi0\li0\qj\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 100\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 -102\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 v\plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24  {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezwrk[0].6930/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 De situatione inferni}}\plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24 , Exzerptsammlung\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 .
\par \pard\fi0\li0\qj\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 De inferno. \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 (a) \plain \f2\lang1024\fs24 [\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 Aufz\u228 \'e4hlung von Quellen:\plain \f2\lang1024\fs24 ]\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 De inferno sunt multe reuelaciones scilicet reuelacio Tundali \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 [vom Schreiber eingef\u252 \'fcgt:\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24  et Brandani\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ]\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 , in libello de purgatorio Patricii. Item in Horologio sapiencie. Item in reuelacionibus Mechthildis \plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24 (\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 wohl {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezper[0].4100/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Mechthildis de Magdeburg}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , s. u. 104\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , 109\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 r\plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24 )\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 . Item in itinerario magistri Johannis de Mandeuelde ... Item in reuelacionibus sancte Brigitte ... Et ubi est situatus expresse et certitudinaliter non habetur.\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ;\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24  \plain \f2\lang1024\fs24 [\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 es folgt Zusammenstellung der Meinungen verschiedener Autorit\u228 \'e4ten:\plain \f2\lang1024\fs24 ]\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  (100\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , 102\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 r\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ) (b) \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 In elucidario suo primo capitulo dicit magister ad discipulum suum: Primo igitur deus constituit sibi palacium, quod dicitur regnum celorum \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ...\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24  - \u8230 \'85 hic in Elucidario\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , (101\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 r-v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ) \plain \f2\lang1024\fs24 [\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 Schaltzettel, s. u.\plain \f2\lang1024\fs24 ]\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ; (102\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 r-v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ) (c) \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 Dauid: Eripuisti animam meam \u8230 \'85 \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 (Ps 55,13).\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24  Infernum vero non irracionabiliter forsitan arbitramur esse sub terris \u8230 \'85 - \u8230 \'85 subterfugit visum nostrum.
\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 (b) {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezper[1].4100/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Honorius Augustodunensis}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezwrk[1].6930/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Elucidarium}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  I,5 und III,3, vgl. PL 172, Sp. 1113B, 1159C-1161C; (c) erw\u228 \'e4hnt werden u. a.: (102\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 r\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ) {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezper[2].4100/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Cassiodorus}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezwrk[2].6930/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Expositio psalmorum}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ; {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezper[3].4100/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Gregorius}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezwrk[3].6930/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Dialogi}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ; {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezper[4].4100/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Ambrosius}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ; {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezper[5].4100/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Johannes Balbus}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezwrk[4].6930/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Catholicon}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ; (102\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ) {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezper[6].4100/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Basilius}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 . }

