\par \pard\fi0\li0\qj\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 Queritur utrum infernus et purgatorium sunt idem. Pretermissis argumentis dicunt doctores quod locus purgatorii est duplex \u8230 \'85\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ;\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24  \plain \f2\lang1024\fs24 [\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 Schaltzettel 103\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 r-v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  s. u.\plain \f2\lang1024\fs24 ]\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ; (104\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 r\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 )\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 \u8230 \'85 \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 (b) \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 Ideo doctor Phalz in una determinacione quotlibetaria dicit sic: Sicut infernus in medio terrrae positus \u8230 \'85 perpetuus iure asseritur materialis.
\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 (a) Erw\u228 \'e4hnt werden u. a. (102\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ) {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezper[0].4100/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Thomas de Aquino}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezwrk[1].6930/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 In IV Sententiarum}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  21,1,1,2; \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 in {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezwrk[2].6930/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 reuelationibus}}\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24  {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezper[1].4100/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 sancte Brigitte}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ;\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24  \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 (104\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 r\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ) \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 in {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezwrk[3].6930/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 reuelationibus}}\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24  {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezper[2].4100/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 sancte Mechthildis}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ; {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezper[3].4100/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Gregorius}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezwrk[4].6930/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Dialogi}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ; (b) {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezper[4].4100/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Johannes von Paltz}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezwrk[5].6930/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Quaestio determinata}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , Conclusio tertia, vgl. Chistoph \plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24 Burger\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  (Hg.), Johannes von Paltz, Opuscula, Bd. 3, Berlin, New York 1989, S. 104.}

