\pard\fi0\li0\qj\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 108\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 r-v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  [Schaltzettel, 11 x 14,5:] {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezper[0].4100/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Johannes Gobi Alestensis Iunior}}\plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24 : {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezwrk[0].6930/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Historia de spiritu Guidonis}}\plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24 ,\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  Exzerpt.
\par \pard\keep\keepn\fi0\li0\qj\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 Prior interrogavit spiritum Gwidonis dicens: Ubi esset commune purgatorium? Respondit spiritus quod in centro terre. ... Item ibidem circa finem dixit spiritus: Ignis infernalis est quoddam corporale \u8230 \'85 \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 (108\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ) \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 \u8230 \'85\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 Item ibidem circa medium valde pulchre declarat spiritus de celebracione misse \u8230 \'85 \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 - \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 ... quam totum officium de requiem. Nota bene.
\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 Druck: Gobi, Johannes, Quaestiones inter Johannem Gobi et spiritum Guidonis. [Leipzig, Konrad Kachelofen, um 1489, vgl. GW 10943, eingesehenes Exemplar: Leipzig, UB, Scr. eccl. 1378/3], aiiii\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 r\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , biiii\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , avi\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 r\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ; zur \u220 \'dcberlieferung vgl. \plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24 Kaeppeli II\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , Nr. 2370; \plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24 Bloomfield\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , Incipits, Nr. 5705; \plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24 Cardelle de Hartmann\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , Lateinische Dialoge, R 46, S. 513-519.}

