\pard\fi0\li0\qj\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 109\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 r\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 -116\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezwrk[0].6930/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 De situatione inferni}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , Exzerpte\plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24 .
\par \pard\fi0\li0\qj\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 (109\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 r\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 -110\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 r\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ) (a) \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 De situacione inferni multe sunt opiniones. In Cecilia \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 (!) \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 est mons Ethna semper ardens, ibidem in eadem insula sunt loca ... Item in reuelacione sancte Mechtildis dicit esse ciuitatem infernalem in abisso profondissima: in deme neddersten abgrunde \u8230 \'85\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ;\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24  \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 (109\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ) \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 \u8230 \'85 Item Plato in Phedone dicitur: \u8230 \'85 Item Johannes Gricz \plain \f2\lang1024\fs24 [\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 = Conradus Gr\u252 \'fctsch, s. u.\plain \f2\lang1024\fs24 ]\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 in sermone feria secunda post Inuocauit \u8230 \'85 \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 - \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 \u8230 \'85 \plain \f2\lang1024\fs24 [\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 Kommentar des Schreibers:\plain \f2\lang1024\fs24 ]\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 Et sic patet de loco inferni ex sacra scriptura Apokalipsis v. et ex scripturas doctorum et ex congruencia racionum efficacium, quod infernus dampnatorum sit iuxta centrum terre. Ego\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  \plain \f2\lang1024\fs24 [\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 Wort gestrichen und interlinear ersetzt durch: \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 non\plain \f2\lang1024\fs24 ]\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 dubito, quando ita sit sicut doctores dicunt scilicet de loco inferni\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ; (b) (110\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 r\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 -112\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ) \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 Nam in legenda sancti Brandani legitur quod ipse nauigauit cum quibusdam fratribus ... \plain \f2\lang1024\fs24 [\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 mit umfangreichen Kommentaren des Kompilators zum Text und zur Authentizit\u228 \'e4t von Visionsliteratur:\plain \f2\lang1024\fs24 ]\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  (111\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 r\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 )\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24  ... Non uidetur michi bene quod legenda sancti Brandani siue sua peregrinacio sit apokrypha \u8230 \'85 Doctores moderni siue et antiqui numquam uoluerunt nec hucusque credere reuelacionibus ac propheciis \u8230 \'85 et multa scripta iudicant apocrypha \u8230 \'85\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ; (112\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 -113\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 r\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ) (c)\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24  Predictus sanctus Patricius in cuius monasterio predictus Paulus heremita dixit se fuisse enutritus \u8230 \'85\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ; (113\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 r\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 -116\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ) (d) \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 Item magister Jacobus episcopus Tusculanus in vita Marie de Onies \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 (!) \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 \u8230 \'85 \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 - ...\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24  et pallacium in celo pulchrum et duos thronos.
\par \pard\fi0\li0\tx4395\qj\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 (a) Zusammenstellung von meist kurzen Exzerpten, u. a. aus: (109\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 r\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ) {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezper[0].4100/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Isidorus Hispalensis}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezwrk[1].6930/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Etymologiae}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  XIV,9,14; (109\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 r\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , 113\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 r\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ) Paraphrasen und Zitate aus{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezper[1].4100/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17  Mechthildis de Magedburg}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezwrk[2].6930/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Lux divinitatis}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , cap. VI,1-6, vgl. Edition (s. o. 104\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ); (109\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 r\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ) {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezper[2].4100/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Augustinus}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezwrk[3].6930/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Quaestionum in heptateuchum libri septem}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  und {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezwrk[4].6930/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 De fide ad Petrum}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs20 , vgl. Schiller, Augustinus, Bd. 2, S. 390 (diese Hs.); \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 (109\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ) {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezper[3].4100/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Plato}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezwrk[5].6930/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Phaidon}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24