\pard\fi0\li0\qj\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 122\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 r-v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezwrk[0].6930/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 De mathematica, astronomia et astrologia}}\plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24 , Exzerptsammlung\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 .
\par \pard\fi0\li0\qj\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 De speciebus mathematice. \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 (a) \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 Mathematica quantitatem abstractam considerat ... Sunt igitur he quatuor species mathematice: Arithmetica tractat de numeris, musica de proporcione, geometria de spacio, astronomia de motu ...\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ;\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24  \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 (b) {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://5650[0].5666l/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Astronomia ut dicit Richardus (!) est disciplina magnitudinis mobilis}}\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24  investigans spatia, motus et reditus celestium corporum\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs20  \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 ...\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ;\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24  \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 (c) \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 Astronomia est astrorum lex, que cursus siderum et figuras et habitudines stellarum \u8230 \'85\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ;\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24  \plain \f2\lang1024\fs24 [\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 am linken Rand:\plain \f2\lang1024\fs24 ]\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  (d)\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24  Alphorabius \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 (!) \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 in libro de diuisione scientiarum: Sciencia doctrinalis id est mathematica in octo partes diuiditur ...\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ; (122\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 )\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24  \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 (e) \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 Inter astronomiam et astrologiam hoc interesse videtur quod astronomia de lege astrorum et conuersione celi disserit regiones, circulos \u8230 \'85\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ; (f) \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 Nota quod dicit Isidorus etymologiarum iii: Inter astronomiam autem et astrologiam aliquid differt \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ...\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24  - \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ...\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24  siderum que cursu natiuitates hominum et mores predicare conantur.
\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 (a) erweiterte Fassung von: {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezper[0].4100/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Vincentius Bellovacensis}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezwrk[1].6930/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Speculum historiale}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , lib. II, cap. 53-55; (b, e) {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezper[1].4100/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Hugo de Sancto Victore}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezwrk[2].6930/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Didascalicon}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  II/16, II/11, III/2, vgl. PL 176, Sp. 757D, 756A, 766B; (b) \u228 \'e4hnliches Incipit in {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://5007[0].501m/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Rom, BAV, Cod. Pal. lat. 1416, 167}}\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , vgl. \plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24 Schuba,\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  Heidelberg UB II, S. 204; (c, f) {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezper[2].4100/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Isidorus Hispalensis}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezwrk[3].6930/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Etymologiae}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  III, 24,1, III,27,1-2; weiterhin Verweise auf (d) {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezper[3].4100/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Alpharabius}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ; (122\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 v\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ) {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezper[4].4100/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Nicolaus de Lyra}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 .}

