\pard\fi0\li0\qj\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 247\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 r\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 -258\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 r\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezper[0].4100/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Vincentius Bellovacensis}}\plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24 : {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezwrk[0].6930/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\b\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Speculum historiale}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , lib. 16, cap. 1-17.
\par \pard\fi0\li0\qj\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 In nomine sancte et indiuidue trinitatis. \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 >\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 De speculo historiali libro xvii \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 (!)\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 .\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 De contemporalitate nouem regnorum et de regno Romanorum\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 <. >{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://5650[0].5666l/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 A<b anno primo Graciani qui fuit ab incarnacione domini}}\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24  ccc\plain \f1\i\super\lang1033\fs24 us\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24  lxxx\plain \f1\i\super\lang1033\fs24 us\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24  i\plain \f1\i\super\lang1033\fs24 us\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24  incipit Sigibertus \plain \f3\lang1024\fs24 [\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 marginaler Vermerk:\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24  >actor Speculi historialis<\plain \f3\lang1024\fs24 ]\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 regnorum contemporalitatem describere ... \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 - \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 ... nunc autem de ceteris sermonem ordinemur.
\par \pard\fi0\li0\qj\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 Gliedernde marginale Notizen und Korrekturen vom Schreiber sowie Nachtr\u228 \'e4ge des {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezper[1].4100/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Johannes de Indagine}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  (247\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 r\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 : \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 Notae sunt Indaginis\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ), von seiner Hand u. a. lokalgeschichtliche Erg\u228 \'e4nzungen, z. B. 249\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 r\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  zu cap. 4: \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 iste Dagobertus fundator monasterii sancti Petri in Erffordia\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  sowie 250\plain \f1\super\lang1033\fs24 r\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  zum Ende von cap. 4 (\plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 ... Ludowicus \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 [IX.] \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 qui adhuc regnat\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ): \plain \f1\i\lang1033\fs24 anno 1244 quando hoc scripsit, sed hodie anno 1454 multi alii reges successerunt. 
\par \pard\fi0\li0\ql\ri0\sb0\sa0\itap0 \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 Druck: Bibliotheca mvndi sev Specvli maioris Vincentii Bvrgvndi praesvlis Bellovacensis, Tomus quartvs, qui Specvlvm historiale inscribitvur, Douai 1624 (ND Graz 1965), S. 618-623. Zur \u220 \'dcberlieferung vgl. {\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezlit[0].8330/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17 Stegm\u252 \'fcller}}{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "hida://bezlit[0].8330/?u"}{\fldrslt \plain \f1\lang1033\fs24\chcbpat17  RB V, Nr. 8304}}\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 ,2,I; \plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24 Kaeppeli\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  IV, Nr. 3987; G. G. \plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24 Guzman\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , A growing tabulation of Vincent of Beauvais\rquote  Speculum historiale manuscripts, in: Scriptorium 29 (1975), S. 122-125; M.-C. \plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24 Duchenne\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  / G. G. \plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24 Guzman\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24  / J. B. \plain \f1\scaps\lang1033\fs24 Voorbij\plain \f1\lang1033\fs24 , Une liste des manuscrits du Speculum historiale de Vincent de Beauvais, in: Scriptorium 41 (1987), S. 286-294.}

